Class FieldLineNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasBoundingArea, HasPosition, HasRotation, HasTransform, IsPickable, TNode, TNode3D, TSceneObject

    public class FieldLineNode
extends Node3D
    provides SceneGraphNode for the management of a FieldLine, includes support for displaying pick shape, symmetry, and line direction markers.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.7 $
    Author:
    Phil Bailey
